law.history: Repealed 1976 (1st Extra. Sess.) Ky. Acts ch. 14, sec. 491, effective January 2, 1978. -- Amended 1968 Ky. Acts ch. 152, sec. 13. -- Amended 1966 Ky. Acts ch. 255, sec. 42. -- Amended 1954 Ky. Acts ch. 197, sec. 1. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. secs. 2914, 3530.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Drunkenness or disorderly conduct -- Disposition in cities of first and fourth classes.
